column2: "Is she okay? What is she doing here?"
"She doesn't look like an ARKS member, but we can't just leave her here like this..."
"Attention all ARKS: Darker activity has dropped to acceptable levels."
"The Code D on Naberius has been lifted."
"All ARKS are to return at once after confirming the safety of their surroundings."
"That's a relief. Looks like we don't have to worry about more Darkers."
"I really don't know what to do about this girl, but someone on the ship should have an idea."
"Well, no reason to stick around here. Let's head back, partner."
